        <abstract>
            <p>Ernst Haeckel wants to go to Ceylon to examine Medusae and Radiolariae, CD has offered him £100.</p> 
<p>Is working on revises of <hi rend="italic">Earthworms</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Has seen a pied flycatcher for the first time.</p>
